          <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 shrink-0" id="rate_unit">per therm</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1" id="rate_hint">US average: $1.20/therm gas, $0.16/kWh electric, $2.50/gal propane</p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex items-end">
        <div class="bg-blue-50 border border-blue-200 rounded-lg p-3 w-full">
          <p class="text-xs text-blue-800">Find your rate on your monthly utility bill — look for the rate per therm (gas) or rate per kWh (electric) in the billing detail section.</p>
